  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Virtual Friend</strong> is a desktop pet/Tamagotchi-like, where you can go through your day accompanied by your favorite character(s). Play with them, or just have them follow what you're doing throughout the day, your friend is always there for you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Always with you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treat your friend like a pet in a box, or disable the window entirely for a truly immersive experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Integrations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My Virtual Friend is compatible with other programs on your computer (can run alongside other virtual pet/wallpaper tools, as well as on top of games). It also knows what you're doing and can change its behavior if you're watching movies, listening to music, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shopping</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of your characters to unlock new clothes, backgrounds, music, characters, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adorable companions:</strong> 4 different, quirky characters to accompany you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable characters:</strong> Personalize your characters' look and interact with them in meaningful ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Focus & Relax:</strong> multiple unique instrumental music playlists designed to help you focus or relax while you work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic integrations:</strong> Your friend reacts to what you're doing on your computer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/abd3de250a1e700748038778a9ad0bc5.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/abd3de250a1e700748038778a9ad0bc5.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/abd3de250a1e700748038778a9ad0bc5.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Virtual Friend</strong> is a desktop pet/Tamagotchi-like, where you can go through your day accompanied by your favorite character(s). Play with them, or just have them follow what you're doing throughout the day, your friend is always there for you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Always with you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treat your friend like a pet in a box, or disable the window entirely for a truly immersive experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/5b0cedda63262d8f309be2ff563210fc.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Integrations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My Virtual Friend is compatible with other programs on your computer (can run alongside other virtual pet/wallpaper tools, as well as on top of games). It also knows what you're doing and can change its behavior if you're watching movies, listening to music, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/ef3c3ab193b3d80773fd19bccd56a2b0.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shopping</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of your characters to unlock new clothes, backgrounds, music, characters, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.webm?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/946f5bbeee21e4571f294bd41d984896.mp4?t=1760575810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adorable companions:</strong> 4 different, quirky characters to accompany you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable characters:</strong> Personalize your characters' look and interact with them in meaningful ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Focus & Relax:</strong> multiple unique instrumental music playlists designed to help you focus or relax while you work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic integrations:</strong> Your friend reacts to what you're doing on your computer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/abd3de250a1e700748038778a9ad0bc5.poster.avif?t=1760575810\" width=60